### English Title:
Trump Says US Will Withdraw from Mediation in Ukraine-Russia Talks if Peace Agreement is Difficult

### English Text Summary:
US President Donald Trump announced that the United States would "withdraw" from mediating further talks regarding the Ukraine-Russia war if either Moscow or Kyiv complicates the peace agreement process. Trump's comments followed warnings from US Secretary of State Marco Rubio about the potential withdrawal from negotiations if peace seems unattainable. The situation remains tense, with ongoing Russian strikes in Ukraine resulting in casualties. Meanwhile, Ukraine and the US have taken initial steps towards a deal concerning minerals, aiming to establish an investment fund for Ukraine's reconstruction. The article highlights the complexities of the negotiations and the challenges in achieving a ceasefire.

